    "Second, the pooling layer is optimized using a parallel structure to cut down on computation.",
    "Furthermore, by smoothing the probability distribution of labels, overfitting is minimized.",
    "Inception V3 is an improved version of Inception V1 and V2.",
    "The idea of Inception V3 was to reduce the computational cost of deep networks without affecting generalization.",
